Project Handover: telos-doctrine-brief

1. User Intent

The user wants a cloud-executable pipeline that:
	1.	Accepts one or more YouTube URLs.
	2.	Fetches transcripts automatically.
	3.	Synthesises them into a structured Doctrine Brief using Claude.
	4.	Runs via GitHub Actions, so it can be triggered from anywhere without local setup.

Primary goal:

Reliable, automated transcript ingestion → Claude synthesis → deterministic output.
No manual transcript retrieval. Fully automated.

Future horizon (post MVP):

Basic web interface allowing users to save their credentials, select language of transcript, input 1+ Youtube URLs

